dc_title_s: Official Indiana: showing counties in different colors, townships, cities, villages, post offices, steam and electric railways with stations and distances between stations.
dc_description_s: Indiana combination edition no. 1324.; Includes Index with populations according to 1930 federal census, population tables, distance chart, chart of land survey system, and inset showing Congressional districts established 1931.; The same map overprinted with roads appears on verso. Scale approximately 1:433,520. 7 miles to 1 inch
